data.title: BIRTHS: Jan. 16 to Jan. 22
data.meta_description: Collin Asche; Laken Bear; Lily Fransen; Jackie Holloway; Alexander Jordan; Landon Quinn; Braylon Sager; Caela Vojack
data.text:
FREEPORT

Collin B. Asche

Benjamin and Krista Asche of Freeport are parents of a son, Collin Benjamin Asche, born Wednesday, Jan. 19, 2011, at FHN Memorial Hospital in Freeport.

Collin has one sister, Alyson, 10, and a brother, Landen, 5.

Grandparents are Randy and Denice Schulz of Freeport and Ronald and Juliet Asche.

LEXINGTON, S.C.

Laken K. Bear

Ryan and Kristi Bear of Lexington, S.C., are parents of a son, Laken Kayser Bear, born Thursday, Jan. 20, 2011, t Lexington Medical Center in Lexington.

Grandparents are Rick and Rose Bear of Freeport and Dennis and Lisa Kayser of Jesup, Iowa.

Great-grandparents are Gene and Marilyn Leopold and Lorraine Stabenow, all of Cedarville, the late Howard Stabenow, Allan and Joan Bear of Orangeville and Bernice Schmitz of Gilbertville, Iowa.

SEYMOUR, WIS.

Lily R. Fransen

Derek and Sarah Fransen of Seymour, Wis., are parents of a daughter, Lily Rebecca Fransen, born Tuesday, Jan. 11, 2011, at Appleton Medical Center in Appleton, Wis.

Grandparents are Clyde and Rebecca Butler of Freeport and Bud Fransen of Byron.

Great-grandparents are Keith and Carolynn Stott of Freeport.

FREEPORT

Jackie D. Holloway

Sadie Smith and Jackie Holloway of Freeport are parents of a son, Jackie Davar Holloway Jr., born Sunday, Jan. 16, 2011, at FHN Memorial Hospital in Freeport.

Jackie has two sisters, Dasáda, 9, and Deshanté, 13, and four brothers, Dalton, 16, Dayton, 15, Draven, 11, and Davánt, 5.

Grandparents are Dorothy Holloway of Freeport, Jack Smith of Los Angeles, Calif., Robin Smith of Freeport and Ricky Smith of Rock Falls.

Great-grandmother is Bessie Smith of Rock Falls.

STOCKTON

Alexander S. Jordan

Steve and Erin Jordan of Stockton are parents of a son, Alexander Steven Jordan, born Saturday, Jan. 15, 2011, at FHN Memorial Hospital in Freeport.

Grandparents are Kristine Brunner, Jerry and Amy Brunner, Debbie Jordan and Michael and Patricia Jordan, all of Stockton.

Great-grandparents are Robert and Thelma Jordan of Stockton, Allen and Virginia Turner of Lena and Esther (Wayne) Wand of Elizabeth.

MONROE, WIS.

Landon C. Quinn

Curtis and Kimberly Quinn of Monroe, Wis., are parents of a son, Landon Curtis Quinn, born Thursday, Jan. 20, 2011, at Monroe Clinic and Hospital in Monroe.

Landon has four sister, Alyssa, 18, Macayla, 15, Loghan, 5, and Lauryn, 2.

Grandparents are Russ and Liz Quinn of Monticello, Wis., Gary and Marsha Wilhelms of Browntown, Wis., and John and Georgia Rizzotto of Lindenhurst.

Great-grandparents are Marta Wilhelms of Freeport and Janeth Johansen of Tucson, Ariz.

LANARK

Braylon A. Sager

Tiffany Phillips and Jonathan Nath-Sager of Lanark are parents of a son, Braylon Allen Sager, born Friday, Jan. 14, 2011, at FHN Memorial Hospital in Freeport.

Braylon has one sister, Brieanna, 17 months.

Grandparents are Sheldon and Robin Phillips of Lanark, and Greg Sager and Tina Kay Pfeiffer-Sager, both of Freeport.

Great-grandparents are Richard and Ruthanne Carter of Milledgeville and Richard and Ada Phillips of Golden Valley, Ariz.

ST. CHARLES

Caela I. Vojack

Aubrey and Chris Vojack of St. Charles are parents of a daughter, Caela Isabel Vojack, born Wednesday, Jan. 12, 2011, at Del Nor New Life Maternity Center in Geneva. Caela weighed 7 pounds 10 ounces, and was 20 inches long.

Grandparents are Steve and Pat Sturtevant of Shannon, Ian and Pat Thomson of Park Ridge and Terry and Sheilia Vojack of Addison.

Great-grandparents are Robert and Donna Schriner of Milledgeville, Ronnie and Donagene Sturtevant of Shannon, Virginia McCallum of Des Plaines and Christopher and Geraldine Kutselas of Niles.
